Author: throwawayedfeelz
Text: Put it this way - if you were faking, you wouldn't feel so bad about two days of eating like that, you wouldn't be worrying about faking, you wouldn't have even considered to restrict so low, not even in the lead up to a planned extra few days for a special, important, sentimental event - you wouldn't lurk around this sub, really. You aren't faking <3
